{
  "stem": "1511.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We used to bake matzos because they were so kosher, my father, that we used to bake matzos in our own place for a lot of the Hasidim.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- you know, I looked at it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was rolling them, and there was girls matched up with [NON-ENGLISH] because there was boys and girls working that were baking matzos for weeks before Pesach.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- so it was a rough time for us, when it came Pesach.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They usually made a pogrom, or they did something bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So one year I remember when we were sitting at the seder-- and usually my father start at 12:00 at night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we had a sleep before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Put on the kettle with the kitchens, and the kids around, and we had to sit and listen everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But some guys came in from, from the city, from outside the holy grounds, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they throw in a dead pig to the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And good enough, they didn't start hitting us or killing us, but it was a big joke.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They start laughing, and they just walked out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After that incident, was a lot, a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When it was a wedding in the city, a Polish wedding, it was a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they always told us they going to kill my father, and they're going to kill everybody, whoever a Jew comes along.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the wedding was in private houses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when they start dancing and one guy take away the bride just to dance, the other one knifed them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the morning, you heard somebody was killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were living like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But specially Jews were very afraid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father went, and we were very scared to live.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
